    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v1 - (0.01 - (v0 + 0.68 / v1 + 0.05)))
    v2 = (((v1 + 0.95 * tmp + 0.31) * v2) - 0.12)
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.sin(v0))
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.cos(v0 + 0.57) / 0.06))
    v0 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.45 * tmp + 0.38)) / v1)
    tmp = (v1 * (wp.exp(v1 + 0.59) + 0.75))
    v2 = 0.55
    data[tid] = v0
